description: Challah! combines traditional Jewish deli food with a farm-to-fork sensibility to create a fresh, homemade and most of all, tasty offering of sandwiches. While the truck is not kosher, it operates in a kosher-style to bring these delicious sandwiches to you.From the Seasonal Brisket to the Matzoh Ball Soup, this rich, wholesome, and soulful comfort food will feel like home.
name: Challah!
